<%= @status_page.name %>
===============================================

✅ INCIDENT RESOLVED: <%= @incident.title %>

All systems are now operating normally.

Final Status: Resolved
Impact: <%= @incident.impact.humanize %>
<% if @incident.components.any? -%>

Affected Components (now operational):
<% @incident.components.each do |component| -%>
  • <%= component.name %> - <%= component.status.humanize %>
<% end -%>
<% end -%>

Incident Timeline:
Started: <%= @incident.started_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %>
Resolved: <%= @incident.resolved_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p %Z") %>
<% 
  duration = Time.zone.parse(@incident.resolved_at.to_s) - Time.zone.parse(@incident.started_at.to_s)
  hours = (duration / 3600).to_i
  minutes = ((duration % 3600) / 60).to_i
%>
Duration: <% if hours > 0 %><%= pluralize(hours, 'hour') %><% if minutes > 0 %> and <%= pluralize(minutes, 'minute') %><% end %><% else %><%= pluralize(minutes, 'minute') %><% end %>
<% if @incident.message.present? -%>

Initial Report:
<%= @incident.message %>
<% end -%>

View the full status page:
<%= status_page_url(@status_page) %>

===============================================

Thank you for your patience during this incident.

You're receiving this notification because you subscribed to updates from <%= @status_page.name %>.

To unsubscribe from these notifications:
<%= @unsubscribe_url %>